<p>Fort, J., &quot;Playboy Panel: The Drug Revolution,&quot;
Playboy, 17(2) : 53-55 et. seq., February, 1970. </p>

<p>Frank, I. M.; Hepler, R. S.; Stier, S.; Rickles, W. H. and
