for December 31 each year. Jail population counts are for June 30
each year. Prisoner counts are for those in custody only. </p>

<p> Because some persons may have multiple statuses, the sum of
the number of persons incarcerated or under community supervision
overestimates the total correctional population. </p>

<p> *Includes convicted and unconvicted adult inmates. </p>

